summary: This statistic shows the number of Major League Baseball players in the united from 2014 to 2017 . In 2017 , the number of participants ( aged six years and older ) in the united kingdom ( uk ) and the number of individuals has been quite stable with a flu on the previous year .
gold: Fast casual restaurant chain Qdoba Mexican Eats had a total of 726 restaurants in 2017 . Of these , 385 were company-owned restaurants and 341 were franchised . This figure steadily increased over the course of the last four years , reaching its peak in 2017 .
